def max_island_area(grid):
    if not grid:
        return 0

    rows, cols = len(grid), len(grid[0])
    max_area = 0

    def dfs(row, col):
        if row < 0 or row >= rows or col < 0 or col >= cols or grid[row][col] == 0:
            return 0

        grid[row][col] = 0  # Mark as visited
        area = 1
        area += dfs(row + 1, col)
        area += dfs(row - 1, col)
        area += dfs(row, col + 1)
        area += dfs(row, col - 1)
        return area

    for i in range(rows):
        for j in range(cols):
            if grid[i][j] == 1:
                area = dfs(i, j)
                max_area = max(max_area, area)

    return max_area
